e. Measuring the DOS of vortex cores in highly tilted\nmagnetic fields with STM can thus be used to study the superconducting gap\nstructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Nov 2017 18:08:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-12"}
